[03:56] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'of the 3D object, Lito tries to capture how the object actually looks from different viewpoints. This matters because real objects don\'t all look the same from every angle, especially for shiny objects or reflections, surface'

[04:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'details, and lighting all change as you move around. So, Lito is designed for 3D reconstruction where the output is not just a rough object, but a more faithful 3D representation that\'s view-dependent.'

