[05:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and the physics and motion are more accurate. All right, so here\'s how it works. Basically, instead of optimizing across the full diffusion trajectory every time, it samples only a single time step in a much smarter way while'

[06:00] [scene:talk]
